Index: Q1|MATCH (node:nss1_Drug) WHERE node.nss4_title is not null RETURN node.iri as entity
Q2|MATCH (node:`nss1_Clinical-Result`) WHERE node.nss4_title is not null RETURN node.iri as entity
Q3|MATCH (node:`nss1_Genetic`) WHERE node.nss4_title is not null RETURN node.iri as entity
Q4|MATCH (p:`nss1_Clinical-Arm`) WHERE p.nss1_description IS NOT NULL RETURN p.iri

Q5|MATCH (p:`nss1_Event-Count`) WHERE p.`nss1_frequency-threshold` IS NOT NULL AND toFloat(p.`nss1_frequency-threshold`) IS NOT NULL AND toString(toFloat(p.`nss1_frequency-threshold`)) = toString(p.`nss1_frequency-threshold`) RETURN p.iri
Q6|MATCH (p:`nss1_Analysis`) WHERE p.`nss1_groups-desc` IS NOT NULL RETURN p.iri

Query: tnode.iri AS tnode_name UNION ALL MATCH (node:nss1_Resource) UNWIND node.`nss1_group-id` AS tnode_name RETURN node.iri AS node_uri
group.iri AS measure_value UNION ALL MATCH (resource:`nss1_Resource`) UNWIND resource.`nss1_measure` AS measure_value RETURN resource.iri AS resource_uri
count_node.iri AS count_value UNION ALL MATCH (resource:`nss1_Resource`) UNWIND resource.`nss1_count` AS count_value RETURN resource.iri AS resource_uri
